<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="no" ?>
<vehicle type="fertilizingSowingMachine" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../../../shared/xml/schema/vehicle.xsd">

    <MR>true</MR>
    <mrPowerConsumer forcePointY="0" forcePointZ="-2.3" />

    <!--

        this equipment model is not "finished", not up to "FS25 standard" : (does it comes from FS19? FS22?)
        missing hydraulics for row unit ground pressure
        missing "cable" for row markers
        missing fertilizer "plumbing"  (there is only one pipe going from the fertilizer tank to the rear of the planter (for filling ? or trailing nurse tank ?)
        missing "plumbing" for vaccum system to each unit
        each row unit is "fixed" (parallelogram is not moving when lifting or lowering the unit on the ground)
        press wheels and planting wheels are not rotating at work
        variable displacement piston PTO pump to reduce tractor hydraulic demands (not represented in game)
        the model is named "4900", and not finished => it seems it was done before FS22 => before 2021 since the 4905 true speed debuted in spring 2021 for the first time IRL

        4000 serie row unit => 8mph max
        this is a "true rate", not "true speed" setup
        13kph max work speed (speed above 10.5kph are not recommended) -> recommended 4 to 6mph

        no brakes !

        this seeder is not equiped for no-till seeding (no-till coulters are required)

        600lbs (272kg) max with trueDepth (not visible here = no hydraulic for row units)
        with spring = 113kg max with duals and 213kg with quads

        no opener for fertilizer

        base weight = 14.3T + fertlizer tank = 14.8T

    -->

